mysql_query: SELECT ( ROUND( (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY D WHERE D.CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = D.ORDER_DATE) / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY) * 100, 2) ) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE
SELECT ( ROUND( (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY D WHERE D.CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = D.ORDER_DATE) / (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY) * 100, 2) ) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE
SELECT 100.0 * ROUND(( SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) / ( SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY) , 4) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE

SELECT CAST((T.IMMEDIATE/T.TOTAL_ORDER_COUNT)*100 AS DECIMAL(18,2)) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM ( SELECT COUNT(1) AS TOTAL_ORDER_COUNT, SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS IMMEDIATE, SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE != CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS SCHEDULED FROM DELIVERY D ) AS T

SELECT IFNULL(ROUND((COUNT(DISTINCT D1.DELIVERY_ID) / COUNT(DISTINCT D.DELIVERY_ID)) * 100, 2), 0) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY D, (SELECT DELIVERY_ID FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) D1
SELECT ROUND (AVG(TIMESTAMPDIFF(DAY,CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE, ORDER_DATE)=0)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND( SUM( ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE )/COUNT(*)*100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY AS D1
SELECT ROUND( SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100 / COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) , 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND( SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)*100/SUM(CASE WHEN DELIVERY_ID IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(( SELECT COUNT(*) IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(((SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID))*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

SELECT ROUND(((SUM(IMMEDIATE_ORDER)/COUNT(*))*100),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM ( SELECT DELIVERY_ID, CASE WHEN (ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS IMMEDIATE_ORDER FROM DELIVERY GROUP BY DELIVERY_ID )TMP
SELECT ROUND((100 * SUM(CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = ORDER_DATE) / COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID)), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND((AVG(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)) * 100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND((COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)/(SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY)*100),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE
SELECT ROUND((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)*100/COUNT(*), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND((SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/ (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE
SELECT ROUND((SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/(SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY)*100,2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE
SELECT ROUND((SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

SELECT ROUND((SUM(CASE WHEN DELIVERY_STATUS = 'IMMEDIATE' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT DELIVERY_ID, CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN IMMEDIATE ELSE SCHEDULED END AS DELIVERY_STATUS FROM DELIVERY) A
SELECT ROUND((SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(*)) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND((SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(ORDER_DATE))*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND((SUM(IF(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE,1,0))/ COUNT(1)) *100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

SELECT ROUND((SUM(SUB.LABEL) / COUNT(SUB.DELIVERY_ID))*100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT DELIVERY_ID, (CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS LABEL FROM DELIVERY) SUB

SELECT ROUND((A.IM/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)*100),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY A JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) AS IM FROM DELIVERY D JOIN DELIVERY DD ON D.DELIVERY_ID=DD.DELIVERY_ID WHERE D.ORDER_DATE=DD.CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) A ON A.DELIVERY_ID=A.DELIVERY_ID

SELECT ROUND((A.IMMEDIATE/B.TOTAL)*100.0, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT COUNT(*) AS IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) AS A, (SELECT COUNT(*) AS TOTAL FROM DELIVERY) AS B

SELECT ROUND((IMMEDIATE_COUNT*100)/TOTAL_COUNT, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT COUNT(*) AS IMMEDIATE_COUNT FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE ) IC, (SELECT COUNT(*) AS TOTAL_COUNT FROM DELIVERY ) AS TC

SELECT ROUND((T1.IMMEDIATE_DELIVERIES / T1.TOTAL_DELIVERIES * 100), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM ( SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) TOTAL_DELIVERIES, SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) IMMEDIATE_DELIVERIES FROM DELIVERY ) T1

SELECT ROUND((TEMP1.N_IMMEDIATE/TEMP2.N_TOTAL)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS N_IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY WHERE CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = ORDER_DATE) TEMP1, (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS N_TOTAL FROM DELIVERY) TEMP2
SELECT ROUND(100 * AVG(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(100 * SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(100 * SUM(D.ORDER_DATE = D.CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) / COUNT(*), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY AS D
SELECT ROUND(100 * SUM(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) / COUNT(DELIVERY_ID), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(100*(B.NUM/COUNT(ORDER_DATE)), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY D, (SELECT COUNT(ORDER_DATE) AS NUM FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) B

SELECT ROUND(100*(IMM/TOT),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT COUNT(*) AS IMM FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) AS IMM1, (SELECT COUNT(*) AS TOT FROM DELIVERY) AS TOT1
SELECT ROUND(100*COUNT(*)/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY D WHERE D.ORDER_DATE = D.CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE

SELECT ROUND(100*COUNT(I.DELIVERY_ID)/COUNT(D.DELIVERY_ID), 2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY D LEFT JOIN ( SELECT DELIVERY_ID FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) I ON I.DELIVERY_ID = D.DELIVERY_ID
SELECT ROUND(100*SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/(COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(100*SUM(IF(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE, 1, 0))/COUNT(*), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(100*SUM(IF(ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE,1,0))/COUNT(*),2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(100*SUM(IMMEDIATE)/COUNT(*),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM( SELECT *, IF(ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE, 1, 0) AS IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY) AS T
SELECT ROUND(100*SUM(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/COUNT(*),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(100*SUM(ORDER_DATE =CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE )/ COUNT( ORDER_DATE ),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY D
SELECT ROUND(100*COUNT(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE NULL END)/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(AVG(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 100 ELSE 0 END),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(AVG(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(AVG(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(COUNT(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN DELIVERY_ID ELSE NULL END)/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(COUNT(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) / COUNT(*)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(COUNT(IF(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE, DELIVERY_ID, NULL)) / COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

SELECT ROUND(COUNT(D2.DELIVERY_ID)/COUNT(D1.DELIVERY_ID)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY D1 LEFT JOIN DELIVERY D2 ON D2.ORDER_DATE = D2.CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE AND D1.DELIVERY_ID = D2.DELIVERY_ID
SELECT ROUND(COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY)*100, 2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE
SELECT ROUND(COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)*100 / (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE
SELECT ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = ORDER_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100 / COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) , 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100 / COUNT(*), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(*) * 100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) * 100 , 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)*100.00/COUNT(*),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(1) * 100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID),4) * 100 AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(IF(ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE,1,0))/COUNT(*)*100,2)IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

SELECT ROUND(SUM(A.IS_IMMEDIATE)/COUNT(A.IS_IMMEDIATE)*100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM ( SELECT *, (CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS IS_IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY) A
SELECT ROUND(SUM(CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = ORDER_DATE)/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

SELECT ROUND(SUM(IMM)/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)* 100 ,2 ) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM ( SELECT DELIVERY_ID , CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS IMM FROM DELIVERY) AS IMM_ORDERS
SELECT ROUND(SUM(IMMEDIATE)/COUNT(*)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY) TEMP
SELECT ROUND(SUM(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) / COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)*100/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(T.TEST)/COUNT(T.TEST)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS TEST FROM DELIVERY) T
SELECT ROUND(T1.COUNTS/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS COUNTS FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)T1

SELECT ROUND(IMM/COUNT(DISTINCT(D.DELIVERY_ID))*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS IMM FROM DELIVERY WHERE DATEDIFF(ORDER_DATE,CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)=0) CNT, DELIVERY D
SELECT ROUND(100*(SUM(T.IMMEDIATE)/COUNT(T.IMMEDIATE)), 2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY) T
SELECT ROUND(( COUNT(*) * 100.00 )/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE
SELECT ROUND(100 * SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(*), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(COUNT(ORDER_DATE)*100/(SELECT COUNT(ORDER_DATE)FROM DELIVERY),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE
SELECT ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)*100/COUNT(*), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND (((SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY))*100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE

SELECT ROUND(100*T2.IMMI_ORDERS / COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) ,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT COUNT(ORDER_DATE) AS IMMI_ORDERS FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) AS T2

SELECT ROUND(COUNT(B.DELIVERY_ID)/COUNT(A.DELIVERY_ID)*100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY A LEFT JOIN DELIVERY B ON B.ORDER_DATE = B.CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE AND A.DELIVERY_ID = B.DELIVERY_ID
SELECT ROUND(SUM(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/COUNT(ORDER_DATE)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

SELECT COALESCE( ROUND(SUM(A.TYPE LIKE IMMEDIATE )/ COUNT(A.TYPE)*100,2) ,0) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM ( SELECT *, CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN IMMEDIATE ELSE SCHEDULED END AS TYPE FROM DELIVERY) A
SELECT ROUND((SUM(IF(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE, 1,0)) /COUNT(DELIVERY_ID))*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

WITH CTE1 AS ( SELECT COUNT(*) AS IMM FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE ), CTE2 AS (SELECT COUNT(*) AS TOTAL FROM DELIVERY) SELECT ROUND(((IMM/TOTAL) * 100),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM CTE1, CTE2

WITH Q1 AS (SELECT DELIVERY_ID, CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN IMMEDIATE ELSE SCHEDULED END AS IMM FROM DELIVERY ORDER BY 1) SELECT ROUND(COUNT(CASE WHEN IMM = 'IMMEDIATE' THEN 1 END)/ COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM Q1

WITH CTE AS( SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS IMMEDIATE_ORDERS FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) SELECT ROUND(CTE.IMMEDIATE_ORDERS/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY, CTE

WITH CTE AS(SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) ,CTE_2 AS(SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS TOTAL FROM DELIVERY) SELECT ROUND(100*IMMEDIATE/TOTAL, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM CTE,CTE_2

WITH CTE AS (SELECT COUNT(*) CNT1 FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE), CTE1 AS (SELECT COUNT(*) CNT2 FROM DELIVERY) SELECT ROUND((SELECT CNT1 FROM CTE)*100/(SELECT CNT2 FROM CTE1),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DUAL

WITH DELIVERY_TYPE AS ( SELECT * , CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN IMMEDIATE ELSE SCHEDULED END AS DELIVERY_TYPE FROM DELIVERY ) SELECT ROUND(COUNT(CASE WHEN DELIVERY_TYPE = 'IMMEDIATE' THEN DELIVERY_ID ELSE NULL END) / COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY_TYPE

WITH IMMEDIATE AS ( SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS CNT FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) SELECT ROUND(IMMEDIATE.CNT/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM IMMEDIATE, DELIVERY

WITH IMMEDIATE_ORDERS AS( SELECT COUNT(*) AS ORDER_COUNT FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE ) SELECT ROUND((ORDER_COUNT/(SELECT COUNT(*) AS TOTAL_COUNT FROM DELIVERY)*100), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM IMMEDIATE_ORDERS

WITH IMMEDIATES AS ( SELECT * FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE ) SELECT ROUND(COUNT(IMMEDIATES.DELIVERY_ID) / COUNT(DELIVERY.DELIVERY_ID) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY LEFT JOIN IMMEDIATES ON DELIVERY.DELIVERY_ID = IMMEDIATES.DELIVERY_ID
WITH T AS ( SELECT CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS IS_IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY ) SELECT ROUND(AVG(IS_IMMEDIATE) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM T

WITH TABLE1 AS (SELECT CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS IMMEDIATE_ORDER FROM DELIVERY) SELECT ROUND(SUM(IMMEDIATE_ORDER)*100/ COUNT(IMMEDIATE_ORDER),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM TABLE1

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT COUNT(*) AS IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE ) SELECT ROUND(IMMEDIATE/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM TEMP, DELIVERY

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT DELIVERY_ID, CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN IMMEDIATE ELSE SCHEDULED END AS ORDER_TYPE FROM DELIVERY ) SELECT ROUND((SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM TEMP WHERE ORDER_TYPE = 'IMMEDIATE') * 100 / (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM TEMP), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT DELIVERY_ID, CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS IS_IMME FROM DELIVERY ) SELECT ROUND(SUM(IS_IMME)/COUNT(IS_IMME)*100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM TEMP

WITH T1 AS( SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS COUNT_IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE ), T2 AS( SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS COUNT_TOTAL FROM DELIVERY ) SELECT ROUND(COUNT_IMMEDIATE/COUNT_TOTAL*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM T1, T2

WITH TEMP AS (SELECT DELIVERY_ID, CUSTOMER_ID, (CASE WHEN CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = ORDER_DATE THEN IMMEDIATE WHEN CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE != ORDER_DATE THEN SCHEDULED ELSE NULL END) AS ORDER_TYPE FROM DELIVERY) SELECT ROUND( (COUNT(CASE WHEN TEMP.ORDER_TYPE = 'IMMEDIATE' THEN 1 END))/(COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID)) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM TEMP
SELECT ( ROUND(100* (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY) ,2) ) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE
SELECT 100*ROUND(SUM(CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE= ORDER_DATE)/ COUNT(*),4) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND( SUM(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) * 100.0 / COUNT(*) ,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/COUNT(*) * 100),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY)) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE
SELECT ROUND(SUM(ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/ (COUNT(*))*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND (( SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY WHERE CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = ORDER_DATE )/ COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)*100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(100 * (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

SELECT CAST( ( COUNT( DISTINCT CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN DELIVERY_ID ELSE NULL END) /COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID) )*100 AS DECIMAL(5,2) ) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT DISTINCT ROUND((SELECT COUNT(ORDER_DATE)*100 FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/ (SELECT COUNT(ORDER_DATE) FROM DELIVERY),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT IFNULL(ROUND(((SELECT COUNT(ORDER_DATE) AS IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) /COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) * 100),2),0) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT IFNULL(ROUND((SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/(SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY)*100, 2), 0.00) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE
SELECT IFNULL(ROUND((SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(CUSTOMER_ID))*100,2),0) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

SELECT IFNULL(ROUND(COUNT(DISTINCT T.DELIVERY_ID) * 100 / COUNT(DISTINCT D.DELIVERY_ID), 2), 0) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT * FROM DELIVERY WHERE DATEDIFF(ORDER_DATE, CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) = 0 ) AS T, DELIVERY AS D
SELECT IFNULL(ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)*100, 2), 0.00) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

SELECT ROUND (COUNT(IMMEDIATE) / (COUNT(IMMEDIATE) + COUNT(SCHEDULED)) *100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT IF (ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE, 'YES', NULL) AS IMMEDIATE, IF(ORDER_DATE <> CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE, 'YES', NULL) AS SCHEDULED FROM DELIVERY) AS NEW
SELECT ROUND( ( COUNT(*) / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY))*100 ,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE
SELECT ROUND( (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE
SELECT ROUND( (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) / (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY)*100, 2 ) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE
SELECT ROUND( (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) * 100 / COUNT(DELIVERY_ID), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND( (SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/ COUNT(DELIVERY_ID))*100, 2)AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND( 100 *COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN DELIVERY_ID ELSE NULL END)/ COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND( COALESCE(((SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 END) / COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) ) * 100),0) ,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND( IFNULL(( SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 END) / COUNT(*) )*100,0),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(((COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) / (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY))*100),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE

SELECT ROUND(((D_COUNT/I_COUNT)*100),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE ) AS D_COUNT, (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY ) AS I_COUNT)T
SELECT ROUND(((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) / COUNT(*)) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(((SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS DCNT FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/(SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS CNT FROM DELIVERY))*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE

SELECT ROUND(((SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID) FROM (SELECT DELIVERY_ID, DATEDIFF(CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE,ORDER_DATE) AS DAYDIFF FROM DELIVERY) AS DD WHERE DD.DAYDIFF <1)/ COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID))*100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(((SUM(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = ORDER_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(*))*100),2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(((SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(*))*100),2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

SELECT ROUND((100*SUM(ORDERS) / COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID, CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS ORDERS FROM DELIVERY) A

SELECT ROUND((A.I/B.T)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT COUNT(*) AS I FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) AS A , (SELECT COUNT(*) AS T FROM DELIVERY ) AS B WHERE 1=1

SELECT ROUND((A.IMMEDIATE/B.TOTAL)*100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT COUNT(*) AS IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) A, (SELECT COUNT(*) AS TOTAL FROM DELIVERY) B

SELECT ROUND((A.SUM1/B.SUM2) * 100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT COUNT(*) AS SUM1 FROM DELIVERY WHERE CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = ORDER_DATE) A, (SELECT COUNT(ORDER_DATE) AS SUM2 FROM DELIVERY) B
SELECT ROUND((COUNT(*) / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY) * 100),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE
SELECT ROUND((COUNT(*)*100/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY)),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE
SELECT ROUND((COUNT(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE=ORDER_DATE THEN 1 END)/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID))*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND((COUNT(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 END)/COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID)) *100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

SELECT ROUND((NUM_IMME / (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY))*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS NUM_IMME FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) TEMP
SELECT ROUND((SELECT 100*COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE
SELECT ROUND((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) * 100 / COUNT(*), 2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/COUNT(*)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY AS T2
SELECT ROUND((SELECT COUNT(CUSTOMER_ID) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/(SELECT COUNT(CUSTOMER_ID) FROM DELIVERY)*100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE
SELECT ROUND((SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS D FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)*100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND((SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) IMMIGIATE_DELIVERY_DATE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/COUNT(*)*100,2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND((SUM( CASE WHEN CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE - ORDER_DATE = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(*) ) * 100, 2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

SELECT ROUND((SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100 / ORDERS.TOTAL), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) AS TOTAL FROM DELIVERY) AS ORDERS
SELECT ROUND((SUM(IF(ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE,1,0)) /COUNT(*)) *100,2)IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND((SUM(IF(ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE,1,0))/COUNT(*))*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND((SUM(IF(ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE,1,0))/COUNT(ORDER_DATE))*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY D

SELECT ROUND(100 * (SUM(I) / SUM(C)), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT CUSTOMER_ID, SUM(IF(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE, 1, 0)) AS I, COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS C FROM DELIVERY GROUP BY CUSTOMER_ID) AS TEMP
SELECT ROUND(100 * SUM(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = ORDER_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(1),2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(100 * IFNULL((SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE), 0) / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE

SELECT ROUND(100 * PART.IMMEDIATE/COUNT(ORDER_DATE), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY D, (SELECT COUNT(ORDER_DATE) AS IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) PART
SELECT ROUND(100 * SUM(IF(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE, 1, 0)) / COUNT(DELIVERY_ID), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(100* (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY) ,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE
SELECT ROUND(100* SUM(ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/COUNT(ORDER_DATE), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(100*(SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

SELECT ROUND(100*A.DELIVERY/COUNT(B.DELIVERY_ID),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY B, (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS DELIVERY FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)A
SELECT ROUND(100*AVG(ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE),2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

SELECT ROUND(100*COUNT(B.DELIVERY_ID) / COUNT(A.DELIVERY_ID), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY A LEFT JOIN (SELECT DELIVERY_ID FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) B ON A.DELIVERY_ID = B.DELIVERY_ID
SELECT ROUND(100*COUNT(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE NULL END)/COUNT(0),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(100*COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE
SELECT ROUND(100*COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)/(SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY),2)AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE

SELECT ROUND(100*SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(1), 2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(100.00 * (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/ (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE
SELECT ROUND(AVG(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = ORDER_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END )*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(AVG(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)*100, 2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(AVG(IF(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE,1,0))*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(AVG(ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE IN (SELECT ORDER_DATE FROM DELIVERY)
SELECT ROUND(COUNT(*) / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY) * 100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE
SELECT ROUND(COUNT(*)*100/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE
SELECT ROUND(COUNT(*)/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY)*100, 2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY D WHERE D.ORDER_DATE = D.CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE
SELECT ROUND(COUNT(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE NULL END)*100/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID), 2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(COUNT(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN DELIVERY_ID END) * 100 / COUNT(DELIVERY_ID), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(COUNT(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE= CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN DELIVERY_ID ELSE NULL END)*100.00/ COUNT(DELIVERY_ID),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(COUNT(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 END)/COUNT(*)*100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(COUNT(CUSTOMER_ID)*100/(SELECT COUNT(CUSTOMER_ID) FROM DELIVERY AS D),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE
SELECT ROUND(COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)*100/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE
SELECT ROUND(COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)/(SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY)*100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE

SELECT ROUND(IMMEDIATE / (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM( SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) D

SELECT ROUND(IMMEDIATE/COUNT(D.CUSTOMER_ID)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT COUNT(A.CUSTOMER_ID) AS IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY A WHERE A.ORDER_DATE = A.CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) AS ABC, DELIVERY D
SELECT ROUND(SUM( (CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) ) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM( ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)* 100/SUM(1),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN DATEDIFF(CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE, ORDER_DATE )=0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(*)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(*), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) * 100, 2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/(SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY) * 100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE= CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)*100.00/ COUNT(DELIVERY_ID),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(IF(ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE , 1 , 0))*100/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(IF(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE, 1, 0))/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID),4)*100 AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY D
SELECT ROUND(SUM(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/COUNT(*)*100, 2)AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(SAMEDATE)/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS SAMEDATE FROM DELIVERY A) A

SELECT ROUND(TEMP.SAMEDAY/COUNT(D.DELIVERY_ID)* 100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY D, (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS SAMEDAY FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE ) AS TEMP

WITH A AS ( SELECT COUNT(*) AS C1 FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE ), B AS ( SELECT COUNT(*) AS C2 FROM DELIVERY ) SELECT ROUND(COALESCE(100*C1/C2, 0), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM A,B
WITH A AS( SELECT (ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE ) AS NB FROM DELIVERY ) SELECT ROUND(SUM(NB)/COUNT(NB )*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM A

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT *, IF(CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE=ORDER_DATE,1,0) AS IMMEDIATE_D FROM DELIVERY GROUP BY DELIVERY_ID ) SELECT ROUND(SUM(IMMEDIATE_D)/MAX(DELIVERY_ID)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM CTE

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT DELIVERY_ID, (CASE WHEN DATEDIFF(ORDER_DATE,CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS FLAG FROM DELIVERY ) SELECT ROUND(SUM(FLAG)/COUNT(FLAG),4)*100 AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM CTE

WITH CTE AS (SELECT *, CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS IMMEDIATE , CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE > CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS SCHEDULED FROM DELIVERY) SELECT ROUND(COUNT(*)*100.00/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM CTE WHERE IMMEDIATE = 1

WITH CTE AS (SELECT COUNT(*) AS C FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE), CTE2 AS (SELECT COUNT(*) AS TOTAL FROM DELIVERY) SELECT ROUND((C/TOTAL)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM CTE,CTE2

WITH CTE AS (SELECT DELIVERY_ID , CUSTOMER_ID , ORDER_DATE , CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE, SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS IMMEDIATE , SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE <> CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS SCHEDULED FROM DELIVERY) SELECT ROUND((IMMEDIATE*100.00)/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM CTE
WITH CTE AS (SELECT DELIVERY_ID, CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS DF FROM DELIVERY) SELECT ROUND(SUM(DF)/COUNT(DF)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM CTE
WITH CTE AS(SELECT CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN IMMEDIATE ELSE SCHEDULED END TEMP FROM DELIVERY) SELECT ROUND(AVG(TEMP = 'IMMEDIATE')*100,2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM CTE

WITH CTE AS(SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS CNT FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE ) SELECT ROUND(((SELECT CNT FROM CTE)/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID))*100 ,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

WITH CTE1 AS ( SELECT * FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE), CTE2 AS ( SELECT COUNT(ORDER_DATE) AS TOTAL FROM DELIVERY) SELECT ROUND(IFNULL(100*COUNT(C1.ORDER_DATE)/C2.TOTAL,0),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM CTE1 C1 CROSS JOIN CTE2 C2

WITH DELIVERY AS( SELECT SUM(IF (ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE,1,0)) AS IMMEDIATE_ORDER , COUNT(*) AS TOTAL_ORDER FROM DELIVERY ) SELECT ROUND((IMMEDIATE_ORDER/TOTAL_ORDER)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

WITH IM AS ( SELECT DELIVERY_ID FROM DELIVERY GROUP BY DELIVERY_ID HAVING SUM(CASE WHEN ABS(DATEDIFF(ORDER_DATE, CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)) = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) = 1) SELECT ROUND((COUNT(IM.DELIVERY_ID)/COUNT(*))*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY D LEFT JOIN IM ON D.DELIVERY_ID = IM.DELIVERY_ID

WITH IMMEDIATE AS ( SELECT ORDER_DATE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE ) SELECT ROUND(COUNT(*) * 100 / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY), 2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM IMMEDIATE

WITH IMMEDIATE_COUNT AS ( SELECT COUNT(*) AS I_C FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE ), TOTAL_COUNT AS ( SELECT COUNT(*) AS T_C FROM DELIVERY ) SELECT TRUNCATE((I_C / T_C * 100),2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM IMMEDIATE_COUNT, TOTAL_COUNT
WITH IMMEDIATE_IND AS ( SELECT CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS IND FROM DELIVERY ) SELECT ROUND(AVG(IND) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM IMMEDIATE_IND

WITH MAIN AS ( SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER() AS NUM FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE ) SELECT CASE WHEN ROUND((SELECT MAX(NUM) FROM MAIN) / (SELECT MAX(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY)*100, 2) IS NULL THEN 0.00 ELSE ROUND((SELECT MAX(NUM) FROM MAIN) / (SELECT MAX(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY)*100, 2) END AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE

WITH T AS (SELECT COUNT(*) AS IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE), A AS (SELECT COUNT(*) AS TOTAL FROM DELIVERY ) SELECT ROUND (IMMEDIATE/TOTAL * 100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM T ,A

WITH T1 AS (SELECT CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE= CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS TOTAL_IMMEDIATE_ORDERS FROM DELIVERY) SELECT ROUND(SUM(TOTAL_IMMEDIATE_ORDERS)/COUNT(TOTAL_IMMEDIATE_ORDERS)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM T1

WITH T1 AS (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) CT1 FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE), T2 AS (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) CT2 FROM DELIVERY) SELECT ROUND((CT1*100)/CT2,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM T1,T2

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT *, COUNT(*) AS CNTIMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) SELECT ROUND( CNTIMMEDIATE/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY)*100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM TEMP

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID) COUNT1 FROM DELIVERY), TEMP2 AS (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID) COUNT2 FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) SELECT ROUND((TEMP2.COUNT2/TEMP.COUNT1)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM TEMP2,TEMP

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT DELIVERY_ID, CUSTOMER_ID, ORDER_DATE, CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE, CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY) SELECT ROUND(AVG(IMMEDIATE)*100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM TEMP

WITH TEMP AS (SELECT *, (CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN IMMEDIATE WHEN ORDER_DATE != CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN SCHEDULED ELSE NULL END) AS STATUS FROM DELIVERY) SELECT ROUND(COUNT(TEMP.STATUS)/( SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY) * 100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM TEMP WHERE TEMP.STATUS = 'IMMEDIATE'

SELECT ( ROUND(100 * (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY AS A WHERE DATE(A.ORDER_DATE) = A.CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY), 2) ) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE

WITH IMMEDIATE_ORDER AS ( SELECT DELIVERY_ID FROM DELIVERY GROUP BY DELIVERY_ID HAVING MIN(ORDER_DATE) = MIN(CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) ) SELECT ROUND(1.0*COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) / (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM IMMEDIATE_ORDER
SELECT ROUND((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY WHERE CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = ORDER_DATE)/(SELECT COUNT(*)*1.0 FROM DELIVERY)*100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE

SELECT ROUND((COUNT(SUB.P)/(COUNT(SUB.DELIVERY_ID)))*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT DELIVERY_ID, ORDER_DATE AS O, CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE AS C, CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE NULL END AS P FROM DELIVERY) SUB
SELECT ROUND((SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(IF (ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE, 1,0))/COUNT(*)*100.00,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/ (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY)*100.0,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE
SELECT ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(ORDER_DATE)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND((SELECT COUNT(CUSTOMER_ID) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE= CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)*100/(SELECT COUNT(CUSTOMER_ID) FROM DELIVERY) ,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE
SELECT ROUND(100*COUNT(*)/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE
SELECT ROUND(((SUM(IF(ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE,1,0)))/COUNT(*))*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

WITH CTE AS (SELECT DELIVERY_ID, CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN IMMEDIATE ELSE SCHEDULED END AS SCHEDULED FROM DELIVERY) SELECT ROUND((SUM(CTE.SCHEDULED = 'IMMEDIATE')/COUNT(*)) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM CTE
SELECT ROUND(AVG(CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = ORDER_DATE) *100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(100*COUNT(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN DELIVERY_ID END)/COUNT(*),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(100*(SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/COUNT(*), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)*100/(SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

SELECT ROUND((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY A INNER JOIN DELIVERY B ON A.DELIVERY_ID=B.DELIVERY_ID WHERE A.ORDER_DATE=B.CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/COUNT(*) * 100,2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(100 * SUM(IF(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE, 1, 0)) / COUNT(1), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT IFNULL(ROUND(100* SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 END)/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID),2),0) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

SELECT ROUND((DAY1.A/COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY.DELIVERY_ID))*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID) AS A FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) AS DAY1,DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND((SELECT 100*COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/ (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY),2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE
SELECT ROUND(SUM(IF(ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE, 1,0))*100/COUNT(*),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(100*COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)/( SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY),2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE
SELECT CAST(100*COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)/(SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY) AS DECIMAL(5,2)) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE

SELECT ROUND(SUM(TEMP = 'IMMEDIATE') / COUNT(TEMP) *100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT (CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN IMMEDIATE ELSE SCHEDULED END ) AS TEMP FROM DELIVERY) AS TAB

SELECT ROUND((TEMP.IMMEDIATE_ORDERS / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY)) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT COUNT(*) AS IMMEDIATE_ORDERS FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) TEMP
SELECT ROUND(COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)/(SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS TOTAL FROM DELIVERY)*100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE
SELECT ROUND(100 * SUM(IF(CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = ORDER_DATE, 1, 0)) / COUNT(*), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
WITH C AS (SELECT COUNT(*) AS IM FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) SELECT ROUND((SELECT IM FROM C)/COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)*100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

WITH NEW AS ( SELECT CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS IMMEDIATE, CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE!=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS SCHEDULED FROM DELIVERY ) SELECT ROUND(SUM(IMMEDIATE)/SUM(IMMEDIATE+SCHEDULED)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM NEW

SELECT ROUND(IMMEDIATE/TOTAL*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM ( SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID) AS TOTAL, SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY) S
SELECT ROUND((SELECT COUNT(ORDER_DATE)*100 FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/COUNT(ORDER_DATE),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

SELECT ROUND((D2.IMMEDIATE/D1.TOTAL) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT COUNT(*) AS TOTAL FROM DELIVERY) D1 JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) AS IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) D2
SELECT ROUND((SUM( CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) / (1.0 * COUNT(*))) * 100 , 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
WITH IMM AS (SELECT COUNT(*) NUM_IMM FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) SELECT ROUND((SELECT NUM_IMM FROM IMM)/COUNT(*)*100,2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN D.CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = D.ORDER_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(ORDER_DATE) *100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY D
SELECT ROUND ( (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)*100/ (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE

WITH ORDER_STATUS AS ( SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NUM_IMMEDIATE , SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE != CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NUM_SCHEDULED FROM DELIVERY ) SELECT ROUND(NUM_IMMEDIATE/(NUM_IMMEDIATE+NUM_SCHEDULED) *100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM ORDER_STATUS
SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(1)*100 AS DECIMAL(5,2)) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/ COUNT(*),4) * 100 AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

WITH TAB1 AS ( SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS SAME_DAY FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) SELECT ROUND(TAB1.SAME_DAY/COUNT(TAB2.DELIVERY_ID)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY AS TAB2,TAB1
SELECT ROUND(100*COUNT(IF(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE, DELIVERY_ID,NULL))/COUNT(*),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

WITH T1 AS ( SELECT DELIVERY_ID, CUSTOMER_ID, ORDER_DATE, CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE, CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN YES ELSE NO END AS IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY ), T2 AS ( SELECT COUNT(IMMEDIATE) AS CYES FROM T1 WHERE IMMEDIATE = 'YES' ), T3 AS ( SELECT COUNT(IMMEDIATE) AS CNO FROM T1 WHERE IMMEDIATE = 'NO' ) SELECT ROUND(T2.CYES/(T2.CYES+T3.CNO)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM T2,T3
SELECT ROUND( (SELECT COUNT(ORDER_DATE) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) * 100 / (SELECT COUNT(ORDER_DATE) FROM DELIVERY), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE
SELECT COALESCE(ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 END)/COUNT(*)*100,2),0) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND( (SELECT COUNT(*) AS IMMEDIATE_ORDERS FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) * 100 / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY) ,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE

SELECT ROUND(SUM(IMM_FLAG)/SUM(TOTAL)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT DELIVERY_ID, CASE WHEN(ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS IMM_FLAG, COUNT(1) AS TOTAL FROM DELIVERY GROUP BY 1) AS M

SELECT ROUND((SUM(A.IMMEDIATE)/COUNT(A.DELIVERY_ID))*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT DELIVERY_ID, CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY)A
SELECT ROUND(SUM(ORDER_TYPE) / COUNT(ORDER_TYPE) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS ORDER_TYPE FROM DELIVERY ) O

WITH IMMEDIATE_COUNT AS ( SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) AS IMMEDIATE_COUNT FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE), TOTAL_COUNT AS ( SELECT COUNT(*) AS TOTAL_COUNT FROM DELIVERY ) SELECT ROUND (100 * ( IMMEDIATE_COUNT/TOTAL_COUNT ),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM IMMEDIATE_COUNT,TOTAL_COUNT
SELECT ROUND(COUNT(*)/(SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE
SELECT ROUND((COUNT(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE NULL END)/COUNT(1))*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND((SUM(IF(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE, 1, 0)) * 100 / COUNT(*)),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT COUNT(*) AS COUNT_IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE ) SELECT ROUND(100*((SELECT COUNT_IMMEDIATE FROM CTE)*1.0 / (SELECT COUNT(*)FROM DELIVERY )),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE
SELECT ROUND(COALESCE( SUM(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE )/COUNT(*) * 100, 0), 2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = ORDER_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND((COUNT(*)/(SELECT COUNT(*) AS NUM_ORDER FROM DELIVERY) )*100, 2)AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT * FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) IMMEDIATE
SELECT ROUND( (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY WHERE CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = ORDER_DATE) / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY) * 100 , 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE
SELECT ROUND(AVG(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)*100.0,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

SELECT COALESCE(CAST((IMMEDIATE *100)/(SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID*1.0) FROM DELIVERY)AS DECIMAL(10,2)),0) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM( SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS IMMEDIATE FROM DELIVERY)A
SELECT ROUND(AVG(A.DEL*100), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM( SELECT CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS DEL FROM DELIVERY ) AS A
SELECT ROUND(100*COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = ORDER_DATE THEN DELIVERY_ID END)/COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT IFNULL( ROUND( 100*COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID)/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY) , 2) , 0) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE
SELECT IFNULL(ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(ORDER_DATE)*100,2),0) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

SELECT ROUND(T1.FIRST_COUNT/T2.SECOND_COUNT * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM ( SELECT DELIVERY_ID, COUNT(*) AS FIRST_COUNT FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE ) T1, ( SELECT DELIVERY_ID, COUNT(*) AS SECOND_COUNT FROM DELIVERY ) T2
SELECT ROUND(COUNT(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = ORDER_DATE THEN CUSTOMER_ID END)*100.0/COUNT(CUSTOMER_ID),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

WITH C AS ( SELECT DELIVERY_ID FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE ) SELECT ROUND(COUNT(C.DELIVERY_ID)/COUNT(D.DELIVERY_ID)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY D LEFT JOIN C ON D.DELIVERY_ID=C.DELIVERY_ID
SELECT ROUND(SUM(IF(ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE,1,0))*100/COUNT(ORDER_DATE),2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND((SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)*100)/COUNT(1),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(IMMEDIATE/TOTAL*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS IMMEDIATE, COUNT(*) AS TOTAL FROM DELIVERY) TEMP
SELECT ROUND(100*(SELECT DISTINCT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE )/(SELECT DISTINCT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY ),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE

SELECT ROUND(((COUNT(CASE WHEN ORDER_PRIORITY = 'IMMEDIATE' THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) / COUNT(*))*100),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM ( SELECT DELIVERY_ID, CUSTOMER_ID, CASE WHEN CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = ORDER_DATE THEN IMMEDIATE ELSE SCHEDULED END AS ORDER_PRIORITY FROM DELIVERY ) SUB
SELECT ROUND( SUM(IF(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE,1,0)) / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY) * 100 , 2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND((SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)*100/COUNT(*)),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(100*(SUM(IMMEDIATE_CNT)/COUNT(*)), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM ( SELECT * ,CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS IMMEDIATE_CNT FROM DELIVERY ) SUB

WITH TMP AS ( SELECT D.DELIVERY_ID, CASE WHEN (D.ORDER_DATE = D.CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) THEN IMMEDIATE ELSE SCHEDULED END AS STATUS FROM DELIVERY AS D) SELECT ROUND(100*SUM(STATUS = 'IMMEDIATE')/ COUNT(*),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM TMP
SELECT ROUND(100.0 * SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1.0 ELSE 0.0 END) / COUNT(DELIVERY_ID), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT CAST(FORMAT((SUM( CASE WHEN DATEDIFF(ORDER_DATE , CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(*) ) * 100, 2) AS FLOAT) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(100.0*SUM((CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END))/COUNT(1),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(A/B * 100,2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT COUNT(*) A FROM DELIVERY WHERE CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = ORDER_DATE) AA , (SELECT COUNT(*) B FROM DELIVERY) S

WITH CTE1 AS (SELECT COUNT(*) AS A FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE), CTE2 AS (SELECT COUNT(*) AS B FROM DELIVERY) SELECT ROUND(A*100/B,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM CTE1, CTE2
SELECT ROUND(100*SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID),2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT DELIVERY_ID, CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS IMMEDIATE_DELIVERY FROM DELIVERY) SELECT ROUND(SUM(IMMEDIATE_DELIVERY)/COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID)*100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM TEMP
SELECT ROUND(SUM(CASE ORDER_DATE WHEN CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(1) * 100, 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(COUNT(*)*100.0/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE
SELECT ROUND((SELECT 100*COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/ COUNT(DELIVERY_ID),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(IFNULL( (SELECT SUM(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) FROM DELIVERY) / (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY),0)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE
SELECT ROUND(((SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/(COUNT(*) * 1.0)) * 100), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND((SUM(ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)/ COUNT(CUSTOMER_ID))*100 ,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND((SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) / (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY)*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE
WITH T1 AS( SELECT CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END TYPE FROM DELIVERY ) SELECT ROUND(SUM(T1.TYPE)*100/COUNT(*), 2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM T1

SELECT ROUND(SUM(IMM_FLAG)/(SUM(SCHE_FLAG)+SUM(IMM_FLAG))*100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM (SELECT DELIVERY_ID, CASE WHEN(ORDER_DATE=CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS IMM_FLAG, CASE WHEN(ORDER_DATE<>CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS SCHE_FLAG FROM DELIVERY GROUP BY 1) AS M
SELECT ROUND (SUM(CASE WHEN ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(1), 2) IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
SELECT ROUND(COUNT(DELIVERY_ID)/ (SELECT COUNT(DELIVERY_ID) FROM DELIVERY) *100,2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY WHERE CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE = ORDER_DATE
SELECT ROUND((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DELIVERY WHERE ORDER_DATE = CUSTOMER_PREF_DELIVERY_DATE)*100 / (COUNT(*)),2) AS IMMEDIATE_PERCENTAGE FROM DELIVERY
